				<li id="16489461" class="cmnt-root" data="5" data-d="1646987105000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578957/Magma-Shot" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">11 Mar 2022 03:25</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16489461" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Tested with 80 Int and 10 Faith on +10 Carian Royal Scepter.<br/><br/>Like Rock Sling, this spell is useful against enemies which resist magic damage. When distances are too short / cramped for Rock Sling, Magma Shot will be more ideal. The projectile has a small AOE so you’re likely to deal full damage to two targets if they’re right next to each other.<br/><br/>Unlike Rock Sling, Magma Shot doesn’t seem to have much stagger - I wasn’t able to knock down trolls with it.<br/><br/>The damage in comparison to Rock Sling ranges from comparable to superior, depending on the enemy. For relatively stationary targets like plants and land squid, the damage is vastly superior to Rock Sling: 1800 to 2500 vs 1000 dmg. The damage varies depending on how many magma pools spawn, and how many pools the enemy is touching.<br/><br/>However this doesn’t necessarily mean that Magma Shot has many use cases outside of magically resistant zombies and possibly claymen (haven’t reached that far yet on NG+). Most relatively stationary targets are also large, and it is far more efficient to use Adula’s Moonblade vs. large enemies. E.g. the land squids I tested on took 4000+ damage from a well placed Adula’s Moonblade.<br/><br/><br/></p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16489461" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16489461" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>8</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>3</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16489461"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16489461" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16489461"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
